author: markt
msg: Correct regression in previous fix for https://bz.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=57136
\$ should be an escape for $ in JSP.
\${ should be an escape for ${ only in EL.
EL rules only apply within an EL expression. The JSP rules apply everywhere else up to and including the ${...} surrounding the expression.
